<h2>What is PhotoStream?</h2>
<p>PhotoStream is an easy way for you to stream live photos at your event. Guests can take photographs using their smart devices, instantly upload them to PhotoStream using a generated Url, and see their images live!</p>

<h2>How to use PhotoStream?</h2>
<p>It's easy! Create an account, set up your event and pass along the photo upload link to your guests.</p>

